                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1845&quot; title=&quot;MultiGet, MultiDelete, and MultiPut - batched to the appropriate region servers&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-1845&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-1845&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; introduced MultiGet and other cross-row/cross-region batch operations.  We should add a way to do that with increments.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
