&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Should you leave Writable in place?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Else LGTM&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13179933" author="lhofhansl" created="Wed, 4 Jan 2012 22:09:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Good point... I just checked, and Row extends WritableComparable, which in turn extends Writable... So should be good.&lt;br/&gt;
Maybe than Append can be simplified to only implement Row and not also Writable.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13179975" author="lhofhansl" created="Wed, 4 Jan 2012 23:18:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch that I committed (based on Stack&apos;s comment Append does not actually need to implement Writable, since Row already extends Writable).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
